~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : ban                                       ~FTPODnuts Revision
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : ban site/user <site or username>

   This command will ban either a site or a user.  For POD application,
   ban has been modified to allow us to filter users from banned domains.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : unban, listbans
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

